      <p>We also use the joy of cooking recipe, with buttermilk.<br />although I have practically abandoned waffles since we found your oatmeal pancake recipe. I recently purchased an electric griddle that has made my pancake making 150% better. when we move into the new house with a gas stove, I&#39;ll be investing in a cast iron skillet. I can&#39;t wait!</p>
