      <p>no other waffle i have ever eaten stacks up to this recipe: <a href="http://eatwithaspoon.blogspot.com/2010/04/waffles.html" rel="nofollow ugc">http://eatwithaspoon.blogspot.com/2010/04/waffles.html</a></p>
