    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>One word: sourdough (to which you can also add chocolate). My dad made them every weekend when I was a kid (or at least he made them on the weekends he didn&#39;t make sourdough pancakes) and they are AMAZING. Only problem is you need a starter. The recipe is in Charles Wilford&#39;s Adventures in Sourdough Cooking and Baking, which I highly recommend if you like sourdough.</p>
