  <li id="comment-16842" class="comment even thread-even depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Lindaf</cite></div>
      <a href="index.html?p=832#comment-16842"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2010-05-14T14:43:42-04:00">Friday, May 14, 2010 at 2:43 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>This is Ingrid Rockwell&#39;s <a href="http://www.thedailypage.com/isthmus/article.php?article=24973" rel="nofollow">waffle recipe</a>. Bon Appetit named her Madison, Wis., food cart, &#8220;Ingrid&#39;s Lunchbox&#8221; the best food cart in the nation a year or two ago&#8230;I&#39;ve made it several times and even without separating the eggs, it&#39;s great.</p>
    </div>

