    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I have made every Cook&#39;s Illustrated waffle recipe ever published (and also your shortbread-become-waffle), and I would definitely agree with those who voted for the recipe with seltzer and buttermilk powder. The first time we made it, my husband looked at me and said, &#8220;This is it.&#8221;</p>
<p>Yeasted are lovely, but they&#39;re really a different animal.</p>
<p>Mark Bittman I have so much respect for but I often feel suckered when I use his recipes &#8212; they&#39;re more-often-than-not just not as good as I imagine.</p>
    </div>

