      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Anonymous</cite></div>
      <a href="index.html?p=832#comment-16861"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2010-05-17T20:27:28-04:00">Monday, May 17, 2010 at 8:27 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>The two recipes that work best for me are the Fanny Farmer Buttermilk Waffles and from the same book the Special Waffles.  The buttermilk recipe calls for 3/4 C melted butter but I can only bring myself to put in 1/2 a cup.  There is no sticking with these babies!  I have made these for family and friends and they are always great.  The Special Waffles work well too.</p>
    </div>

